{"tid":2083895,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"保安局確認警方6月1日青山靶場訓練曾用催淚煙","createTime":"2020-06-29T05:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T05:19:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8f9aed005e0a1ce8b3a317a404c6efc83f4bb320","tid":2083895,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:00:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534652-20200629.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534652-20200629.htm&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8VwLDRbgpiba54y0vEBNjMo%3D&h=d8973449\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534652-20200629.htm&h=b88376d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534652-20200629.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n保安局確認，警察機動部隊總部在本月一日在青山靶場作恆常訓練，期間曾使用催淚煙，因應當日風向影響，催淚煙可能被吹到流浮山一帶。<br />\n<br />\n保安局回覆立法會，表示消防處當日下午2時許先後收到兩宗報告，指流浮山上白泥等地方懷疑傳出不明氣味，但都沒有發現不尋常氣味，一共有7人報稱因吸入不明氣味後曾感到不適。<br />\n<br />\n保安局說，為提升警員面對不同情況的應變能力，警隊一直會定期安排演練，警方會繼續與相關部門和區內居民加強溝通，將對公眾造成的不便減至最低。<br />\n<br />\n警方當日回覆傳媒時，無提及催淚煙，表示因風向影響，以致<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「訓練煙」</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />飄向上白泥及下白泥一帶。而警察機動部隊當日在青山靶場進行恆常訓練，期間人員使用的彈藥裝備均為恆常訓練所用。"},{"pid":"a173df95cd30fb20120d5c8979cfcf33b0161225","tid":2083895,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:04:28.000Z","msg":"97前試過，警隊道歉<br />\n97後，道歉真係天方夜譚"},{"pid":"505b3994abd220d99a98761340095e7866f3a0c0","tid":2083895,"uid":46213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:05:55.000Z","msg":"會唔會毒死流浮山d刀手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c7be46dafa231642fdaba93a6b7874c140b11c","tid":2083895,"uid":231480,"like":0,"